        <meta charset="utf-8">
<p>Nestled in our gorgeous vineyard estate in Akluj lies a harbour. A harbour for those who desire an escape from the noise of our fast-paced cosmopolitan lives. A harbour for those who wish to immerse themselves deeply in the loving caress of our vineyards. A harbour for you.</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0491/6628/7016/files/story_escape_1_1024x1024.jpg?v=1604574166" alt=""></p>
<p>Nurture your soul and heal your spirit as you soak in the goodness of our hidden sanctuary.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Pamper yourself with the best of wine, food and nature in our guesthouse - your home away from home.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Visit our cellars for a tasting of our various vintages and enjoy lovingly prepared authentic Maharashtrian cuisine, and a variety of others too, from our wonderful chefs…</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0491/6628/7016/files/story_escape_2_1024x1024.jpg?v=1604574231" alt=""></p>
<p>Create memories for a lifetime with your friends and family, or treat your special one to the weekend getaway they deserve. After all, there is very little that is more romantic than a vineyard in the evening.</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0491/6628/7016/files/story_escape_3_1024x1024.jpg?v=1604574260" alt=""></p>
